  "original_title": "\u0baf\u0bbe\u0bb4\u0bcd \u0bae\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b9a\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bcb\u0ba4 \u0b8e\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bca\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0baa\u0ba9\u0bc8 \u0ba8\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bae\u0bcd \u0b9a\u0bc1\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0bb1\u0bbf\u0bb5\u0bb3\u0bc8\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Illegal fuel outlet raided in Jaffna Mandigai",
      "author": "Digital Desk 5",
      "body_lines": [
        "10 liters of petrol and 20 liters of diesel (12) have been seized from the house of a person involved in the sale of illegal fuel in Jaffna's Mandigai Puloli area on Tuesday around 5:30 pm.",
        "Based on the secret information received by the Perdutura police investigation unit, when the search was conducted there, 10 liters of petrol and 20 liters of diesel were seized in 10 bottles of 1.5 liters and the Perdutura police are conducting further investigations for appropriate legal action.",
        "It is worth mentioning that the person involved in the illegal sale of fuel is a road driver.",
        "At the same time, 450 liters of diesel and kerosene seized from the house of a retired bank manager in Tumbalai area of \u200b\u200bParuttura has been handed over to the Puloli filling station, which was provided for essential needs in the name of the order of the Paruttura Magistrate Court."
      ],
